import styled from "styled-components"

const Container = styled.div``

export const Login = () => {
    return (
        <Container>
            <Wrapper>
                <Title>SIGN IN</Title>
                <Form>
                    <Input placeholder="username" />
                    <Input placeholder="password" />
                    <Link>DO NOT YOU REMEMBER THE PASSWORD?</Link>
                    <Link>CREATE A NEW ACCOUNT</Link>
                    <Button>LOGIN</Button>
                </Form>
            </Wrapper>
        </Container>
    )
}
